criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          1. Patients diagnosed with COPD in 2015;

          2. Patients had complete hospital visit data available during pre-index 1 year period and
             post 1 year follow-up;

          3. Patients had at least one COPD exacerbation during 1 year prior to the index date;

          4. Patients had at least 2 COPD maintenance medication claims during post index 1 year
             period, as 2 claims are recommended to calculate adherence.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          1. Inability to determine diagnoses from claims;

          2. Individuals with other chronic respiratory conditions such as respiratory cancer,
             pulmonary fibrosis, asthma.
